title: Childhoods End - Two part dramatisation
description:
A dramatisation of the novel by Arthur C Clarke.

The overlords are an apparently all powerful, but benign group of alien beings who invade Earth. They choose not to reveal themselves to the people of Earth, though their leader forms a close bond with the Secretary General of the UN. They give great wisdom to the people of Earth, but will not tell them how their craft travel huge distances through space.

As time goes on though, their true intentions start to become clearer......
